# ── Quote form email delivery (Resend) ───────────────────────────────
# The /api/quote route emails new leads. Without a key it still works:
# submissions are logged server-side and the user sees a success message.
# To actually deliver emails, create a free account at https://resend.com,
# verify your sending domain, and set:

RESEND_API_KEY=
# Inbox that receives quote requests (defaults to the address in src/lib/site.ts)
QUOTE_TO_EMAIL=blackironcleanoutsllc@gmail.com
# Verified sender (must be on a domain you verified in Resend)
QUOTE_FROM_EMAIL="Black Iron Cleanouts <quotes@yourdomain.com>"
